Subject: Re: [T2] having trouble opening my slidding door

On Mon, 2 Jul 2007, sam josovitz wrote:

> hey type2 family since your talking about slidding doors i am having trouble
> opening my sliding door and to close it i have to put muscle into it what can
> i do to make it easier to open my slidding door.

Might be that your rollers are siezed up.  See if they are actually
rolling when you move the door.  If so, remove, relube or replace.

You also might have problems with the lower guide being rusted through.
Let's hope that isn't the case.
